I just bought Meowkai today, and so far I&#039;m definitely loving it! {{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}} 

One problem though... the emotes are cute and all, but apparently the classic Maokai&#039;s emotes play sometimes as well. If you try walking and laughing it will play the classic Maokai&#039;s laugh. It&#039;s very strange and I hope it&#039;s fixed. (Not sure if Riot will notice this anyways :c)

